promoterAddress: OPP. SRP CAMP, VARDHMANNAGAR, NEW 150 FEET RING ROAD, GHANTESHWAR Rajkot 360006

formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1. This certificate is issued based on provisional books of accounts as on 30th April, 2021 as provided to us by promotors.
2. At Point No. 7 of the certificate actual withdrawal from RERA account is Rs. 4,42,70,760/- till 30.04.2021. However as it exceeds the limit of total amount which can be withdrawn at Point No. 6. Accordingly on calculation figure at point no. 8 goes negative. As negative figure is not accepted while online filing of Form 3 on RERA portal, maximum figue allowed at Point No. 7 i.e. 4,28,42,215/- is entered for better compliance.
3. BU Permission (Completion Certificate) has been obtained on 02.07.2020. Accordingly no further major expense shall be incurred in the project. Thus, after receipt of completion certificate all amount as deposited in RERA Account has been withdrawn.  Due to this reason only total withdrawal from RERA account exceeds the limit as aforesaid. Further, as per clarification received from promoters society registration is under process. Once the society is registered QE of the project shall be duly filed.

4.  In Annexure to CA Certificate (Form 3A), in the column "Date of Agreement of Sale",  date of Agreement of sale or Date of Sale deed as applicable in particular case is provided.
5. In Annexure to CA Certificate (Form 3A), some units are booked where payment more than 10% has been receive, however Agreement to sale has not been executed. The management have given explanation that, allottee has given written request to Promotor that allottee is not sure about in whose name document to be executed, so till the name is  finalized do not execute the agreement to sale.
6.  In Annexure to CA Certificate (Form 3A), in the column"Mobile Number of Allottee" as per request of promoters, contact number of Promotor is provided due to security reasons.
